article.headline: Stetson 76, Lipscomb 68
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- Garfield Blair scored 22 points to lead Stetson in a 76-68 win over Lipscomb on Monday night. A.J. Smith added 16 points and Sheldon Oliver chipped in with 10 for the Hatters (6-6, 3-1 Atlantic Sun Conference). Adnan Hodzic led the Bisons (6-7, 2-2) with 19 points and Brian Wright scored 12. Stetson shot 39.7 percent from the field (25 of 63) compared to a 49 percent mark (24 of 49) for Lipscomb, but the Hatters capitalized on 20 turnovers en route to victory. Neither team shot well from beyond the arc as Stetson hit just 7 of 24, while Lipscomb was 5 of 19. The Hatters led by four at halftime and held off the Bisons in the second half, outscoring them 40-36.
